name: Zubos Management System
body:
### Zubos Management System
I have no idea why I named it zubos, it was the first thing that came into my head. Anyways, this is an ongoing project by just myself for just learning purposes and experience; which may or may not go on to being sold on the internet to small businesses etc. (probably not).

### Support or Contact
No need for this just yet.
